that sometimes music

01:32:41.340 --> 01:32:46.580
that isn't explicitly political,
music that might even strike some

01:32:46.580 --> 01:32:52.320
as trite, can nevertheless
do political work,

01:32:52.320 --> 01:32:55.640
take for example Sister
Sledge's "We Are Family".

01:32:55.640 --> 01:32:59.950
A track that ignited dance
floors, believe me, it was the song

01:32:59.950 --> 01:33:03.430 position:56%
