get people out in the dance floor.

01:33:03.430 --> 01:33:07.720
But it also was the song that
kept Nelson Mandela going

01:33:07.720 --> 01:33:11.040
when he was in prison.

01:33:11.040 --> 01:33:15.730
Now, I'm not knocking songs such
as "Ohio" by Crosby, Stills,

01:33:15.730 --> 01:33:18.620
