need not be overtly political

01:33:23.000 --> 01:33:28.580
to get people feeling, moving,
and even thinking differently.

01:33:28.580 --> 01:33:32.690
And I think what disco offers
us is a case study of the ways

01:33:32.690 --> 01:33:37.820
