understood as a social process.

01:33:37.820 --> 01:33:43.410
Through it, we learn in fact how
to experience our own feelings,

01:33:43.410 --> 01:33:48.430
our own desires, and
sometimes even our own bodies.

01:33:48.430 --> 01:33:52.820 position:56%
And this is why when thinking about
music, it's important to acknowledge

01:33:52.820 --> 01:33:57.390
that music not only reflects what's
happening politically, culturally

01:33:57.390 --> 01:34:01.100 position:56%
