01:38:37.050 --> 01:38:40.390
And in the book, I argue that
disco broaden the contours,

01:38:40.390 --> 01:38:42.840
the contours of identity
in three areas.

01:38:42.840 --> 01:38:46.370
First of all, disco
evolved out of the work

01:38:46.370 --> 01:38:50.840
