very clever segues that fooled you

01:48:29.590 --> 01:48:34.770
into thinking that you were dancing
to the last song, not the new one.

01:48:34.770 --> 01:48:39.280
Seamless music signaled I
think a break with the past,

01:48:39.280 --> 01:48:43.020
a break with those nights when
a flashlight or a red light

01:48:43.020 --> 01:48:47.920 position:56%
