sheer relentlessness

01:48:50.200 --> 01:48:55.090
of this music obliterated
shyness and inhibitions

01:48:55.090 --> 01:48:56.880
and a good disco sound system

01:48:56.880 --> 01:49:00.110
which emphasized the music's
thunderous base was like,

01:49:00.110 --> 01:49:05.040
as one person put it,
an audio orgasmatron.

01:49:06.130 --> 01:49:10.070
And the sweatbox conditions of
many discos ushered in the era

01:49:10.070 --> 01:49:13.240
