one of the central issues

02:18:31.710 --> 02:18:37.140
of our time is we have a kind of
microeconomy, which is deeply sort

02:18:37.140 --> 02:18:41.680
of fueled by new technologies
and music exacerbated

02:18:41.680 --> 02:18:44.870
by what one might call the
MP3 effect after Napster,

02:18:44.870 --> 02:18:49.990 position:56%
which means the genie of the
commodity form got out of the bottle

02:18:49.990 --> 02:18:51.840
in some ways and became free.

02:18:51.840 --> 02:18:56.770 position:56%
And we have a paradoxically now in a
period of time where the commodity,

02:18:56.770 --> 02:19:01.920
the debased rational segmented
musical sounds are in a sense free

02:19:01.920 --> 02:19:05.000
and it's the concepts that
have become very expensive.

02:19:05.000 --> 02:19:08.080
