of are, in some sense,

02:34:29.000 --> 02:34:31.200
at war with some social project.

02:34:31.200 --> 02:34:32.500
&gt;&gt; Alice Echols: Yeah.

02:34:32.500 --> 02:34:33.880
&gt;&gt; Martin Scherzinger: In fact,
