liberation more or less.

02:34:39.770 --> 02:34:43.290
I think it's deeply
mired in social sort of--

02:34:43.290 --> 02:34:48.390
and cultural icons and symbols
that are mobilized on television

02:34:48.390 --> 02:34:52.120 position:56%
and then later online and so on,
you know, "Modern Family" and so on.

02:34:52.120 --> 02:34:53.760
And that played a rule.

