02:41:09.610 --> 02:41:14.020
I see Nona Hendryx
and all of them and--

02:41:14.020 --> 02:41:18.250
but I didn't see that clear
distinction at all of sort of merge

02:41:18.250 --> 02:41:21.140
and that's why I kind of
agree-- I agree with her too,

02:41:21.140 --> 02:41:23.470
that I don't think
