a trombone, they would use

02:42:31.850 --> 02:42:33.350
like the flugelhorn or something.

02:42:33.350 --> 02:42:37.930 position:56%
And I think would use different,
different sounds and they were going

02:42:37.930 --> 02:42:40.990
for a more deliberately
sophisticated sound.

02:42:40.990 --> 02:42:44.840
And so that was why I was
saying that, in some sense,

02:42:44.840 --> 02:42:48.840
you can understand what they
were doing as an active rebellion

02:42:48.840 --> 02:42:52.730
against the notion that soul music
had to sound a particular way.

02:42:52.730 --> 02:42:56.190
One of my favorite quotes is
from Mary Wilson of the Supremes

02:42:56.190 --> 02:43:00.380
