02:43:32.320 --> 02:43:33.620
&gt;&gt; Right.

02:43:33.620 --> 02:43:35.740
&gt;&gt; Alice Echols: And to really
sell to white Americans,

02:43:35.740 --> 02:43:39.580
but not in a way that-- in my view,

02:43:39.580 --> 02:43:42.610
not in a way that compromised
that music.

02:43:42.610 --> 02:43:45.250
That music was soulful.

02:43:45.250 --> 02:43:48.960
Motown music was soulful
and disco music was soulful.

02:43:48.960 --> 02:43:50.260
&gt;&gt; Right.

02:43:50.260 --> 02:43:52.330
&gt;&gt; Alice Echols: But I think
it is very, very difficult.

02:43:52.330 --> 02:43:55.910
I mean, to try to actually,
