the extent of which we try

02:44:05.530 --> 02:44:10.500
to create this very narrow
sort of categories for disco

02:44:10.500 --> 02:44:14.060
and what constitutes disco, when
that's not true for rock music.

02:44:14.060 --> 02:44:15.360
&gt;&gt; Right.

02:44:15.360 --> 02:44:16.660
&gt;&gt; Alice Echols: You know, you say,

02:44:16.660 --> 02:44:19.540
punk rock is considered
rock music, right?

02:44:19.540 --> 02:44:23.740
You could say blues
rock is country rock.

02:44:23.740 --> 02:44:25.440
But it's considered rock.

02:44:25.440 --> 02:44:28.810
I mean, nobody is trying
to cordon it off and put it

02:44:28.810 --> 02:44:32.650
in its own little box,
