So, I take the expansive view.

02:45:03.040 --> 02:45:04.350
&gt;&gt; Yeah, that's right.

02:45:04.350 --> 02:45:05.650
Thank you.

02:45:05.650 --> 02:45:06.950
&gt;&gt; Martin Scherzinger: To
