about how the beat is organized.

02:45:17.510 --> 02:45:21.010
And I think this prominence
again of the open high hat

02:45:21.010 --> 02:45:22.680
in between the dominant beat.

02:45:22.680 --> 02:45:23.980
&gt;&gt; Alice Echols: Yeah.

02:45:23.980 --> 02:45:25.280
&gt;&gt; Martin Scherzinger: So that
