02:45:36.730 --> 02:45:39.110
down against the main beat,
has sort of accelerating,

02:45:39.110 --> 02:45:41.960
decelerating effect
within that environment.

02:45:41.960 --> 02:45:45.040
And that becomes, I think, a
dominant feature of how a beat--

02:45:45.040 --> 02:45:46.550
how the beat, if that's--

02:45:46.550 --> 02:45:48.650
just technically about how
